(1, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS 650D (18-55)', 'gambar/eos650d-b5.png', 4, 6400000, '<p><span style=\"background-color: #ff6600;\"><strong>Garansi: Datascrip</strong></span><br /><br /><br />The EOS 650D promises unparalleled performance with the world\'s* first intuitive touch screen (vari-angle) interface for set-shoot-view convenience. Its Auto-focus (AF) System is precise with a new 9-point all cross-type AF backed by a new Hybrid CMOS AF System. AF speeds are dramatically increased while focusing on live view and movie shooting modes.<br /><br /> ISO 100-12800, expandable to 25600<br /> Handheld Night Scene<br /> Continuous AF in Movie Mode<br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> World\'s first Vari-Angle Clear View LCD II Touch Monitor</span></strong><br /><br /> With the intuitive set-shoot-view vari-angle LCD touch screen monitor, it\'s easy to adjust exposure and shutter speeds quickly. Auto-focusing in live view mode is activated by tapping the subject on the LCD. A Touch Shutter option activates the shutter on tapping on the area to be focused. Perform familiar multi-touch gestures to zoom in and out of shots, view images and flip pages.<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong> Hybrid CMOS AF System</strong></span><br /> <br /> During live view and movie shooting, EOS 650D uses both conventional Contrast AF and new Phase Difference AF in conjunction with continuous AF to quickly focus on a subject even before the shutter is pressed. <br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> Choose from 4 different AF methods:</span></strong><br /><br /> &middot; Face + tracking<br /> &middot; rack a face, even in side profile with the EOS 650D. AF points can also be switched simply by touching the subject on the LCD monitor<br /><br /> &middot; FlexiZone &ndash; Multi<br /> &middot; The EOS 650D intuitively selects the appropriate focus from 31 AF points. Touch the LCD monitor on any of the 9 AF zones to fine-tune auto focus.<br /> <br /> &middot; FlexiZone &ndash; Single<br /> &middot; Touch anywhere on the LCD monitor to move the AF point<br /> <br /> &middot; Quick mode<br /> &middot; Select any of the 9 AF point unlike conventional focus mechanisms by selecting the area on the LCD panel <br /><br /> Enhanced Movie shooting with Movie Servo AF Movie servo is possible with all lenses. But the new EF-S18-135mm f/3.5-5.6 IS STM lens is geared for movie shooting; users enjoy smooth, speedy and quiet Servo AF on EOS 650D during movie shooting.</p>'),
(2, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot A2500', 'gambar/powershota2500-b8.png', 3, 1000000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">Make Every Moment Special</h2>\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">The PowerShot A2500 is a stylish compact camera that makes capturing amazing images simple without compromising on quality. The new ECO Mode allows you to capture more shots per charge. The versatile PowerShot A2500 is available in black, silver and red.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>16 MP</span></li>\r\n<li><span>28 - 140mm</span></li>\r\n<li><span>10x ZoomPlus</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Eco Mode</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Eco Mode</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The new ECO Mode provides more shots per single charge and is easily activated via a dedicated button. The ECO Mode also quickly wakes the camera from sleep when a button is pressed so you won\'t miss any precious moment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Auto HELP button</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Designed to be fun and easy to use, even to the beginners the PowerShot A2500 incorporates the AUTO Help button that brings up a quick reference help menu any time you need it. Offering you advice with clear explanations and diagrams on a variety of topics.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Digital IS</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Digital IS beats the blur that mars many shots by recognizing the main subject, then automatically applying the camera shake correction that best suits the situation.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
(3, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot A2600', 'gambar/powershot-a2600-b8.png', 2, 1200000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">Capture the fun in life</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Advanced capabilities coupled with chic design sets the PowerShot A2600 apart from the crowd. This new PowerShot A-Series is equipped with a 5x Optical Zoom and 10x ZoomPlus to get you closer to the action fast. This chic, compact camera is available in black, silver and pink.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>16 MP</span></li>\r\n<li><span>28 - 140mm</span></li>\r\n<li><span>10x ZoomPlus</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Eco Mode</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Eco Mode</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">By reducing the LCD screen brightness gradually until it switches off when the camera is not in use, the ECO mode saves battery consumption and allows you maximized photo opportunity - up to 30% more photos!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Auto HELP button</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Designed to be fun and easy to use, even to the beginners the PowerShot A2600 incorporates the AUTO Help button that brings up a quick reference help menu any time you need it. Offering you advice with clear explanations and diagrams on a variety of topics.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Large 3\" LCD</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Whether you\'re shooting, reviewing or sharing your images with your friends and family. This high-resolution screen offers crisp, clear and bright images on a large 3\" LCD screen.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(4, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS 600D (18-55)', 'gambar/eos600dkit1-b2.png', 1, 5450000, '<p>Garansi: Datascrip<br /><br /><br />The EOS 600D is powered by an 18-megapixel high image quality CMOS sensor and the powerful DIGIC 4 image processor. Features like Scene Intelligent Auto, Basic+ and Feature Guide make it simple to achieve full control over creative functions. The advanced Creative are integrated into the EOS 600D, as well as Full HD video recording and Video Snapshot. <br /><br /> 18.0 megapixel APS-C size CMOS sensor<br /> ISO 100-6400, expandable to 12800<br /> Full HD recording in 24, 25 and 30fps<br /><br /> Class-leading 18.0-megapixel CMOS sensor<br /><br /> In the spirit of Canon\'s imaging supremacy, the EOS 600D adopts a generous 18-megapixel CMOS (APS-C-sized) sensor that empowers you to take all manner of scenes from vast, breathtaking landscapes to close-up wildlife shots in explicit detail. Having a massive 18-megapixel resolution also means that you can still turn your photos into gallery exhibits even after cropping them.<br /><br /> 3-inch wide Vari-Angle clear view LCD monitor<br /><br /> For exceptional recording and playback of images, the EOS 600D employs a crisp 3-inch wide Vari-Angle Clear View LCD monitor that contains over a million dots. The nifty Vari-Angle screen is also a welcome addition for curious shutterbugs looking to discover fresh framing perspectives, as the specially designed hinge allows it to be swivelled in almost any angle.<br /><br /> Scene Intelligent Auto<br /><br /> Fresh out of Canon\'s factory of innovation is the Scene Intelligent Auto mode, a fully automatic shooting mode that takes total advantage of the EOS Scene Detection System, an integrated system that analyzes every element of a scene including a person\'s face, and/or the image\'s brightness, movement, contrast, colour, distance and more. This information is then expertly evaluated by Scene Intelligent Auto to produce beautiful exposures that truly capture the essence of their surroundings.</p>'),
(5, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot SX160', 'gambar/sx-160-is-b1.png', 1, 1750000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">Experience the Power of Telephoto</span></h2>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\">The PowerShot SX160 IS is the perfect combination of camera and that of an extraordinary video maker. Videos are recorded in spectacularly detailed 720p HD with clear stereo sound. Better yet, you can now zoom in and out as your creativity demands, without losing a bit of the 720p HD resolution. Given the SX160 IS\'s powerful 16x Wide-Angle Optical Zoom, this capability is especially meaningful. </span></p>\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\">16 megapixels </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\">16x Optical Zoom </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\">32x Zoom Plus </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2 align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">16x Optical Zoom with f3.5 (w)</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\">A powerful 16x Optical Zoom (28-448mm) provides a wide range of shooting possibilities that are great for travelling and day to day photography.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2 align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">Intelligent IS</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\">The camera automatically selects the optimum IS for all situations allowing users to capture crystal-clear, picture-perfect moments whether if they are capturing photographs or video.<br /> <br /> The Intelligent IS eliminates shake by analyzing the motion of both the camera and subject, and identifies the shot type such as panning, macro or telephoto shot. </span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2 align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana; font-size: small;\">LIVE View Control</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\">LIVE View Control allows users to make adjustments such as exposure compensation, white balance, contrast, and sharpness and be able to see the differences in real time on the LCD display prior to shooting the photograph.</span></p>\r\n</div>'),
(6, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot SX500', 'gambar/sx-500-is-b1.png', 1, 2800000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">The Power to Be Closer</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Fits into any small bag, this ultra compact PowerShot SX500 IS features a telephoto zoom of up to 30x Optical Zoom. The Intelligent IS and zoom framing assist feature help locate and capture your desired subject in perfect clarity.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>16 megapixels</span></li>\r\n<li><span>30x Optical Zoom</span></li>\r\n<li><span>High Speed AF</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Ultra-Slim Telephoto Camera</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The ultra-compact PowerShot SX500 IS is loaded with a powerful 30x wide optical zoom (24 &ndash; 720mm) and professional-style manual controls to capture stunning images quality in all shooting situations.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Intelligent IS</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The camera automatically selects the optimum IS for all situations allowing users to capture crystal-clear, picture-perfect moments whether if they are capturing photographs or video. <br /><br />The Intelligent IS eliminates shake by analyzing the motion of both the camera and subject, and identifies the shot type such as panning, macro or telephoto shot.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Zoom Framing Assist &ndash; Seek</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">At maximum telephoto, it can be very difficult to track a moving subject. Zoom Framing Assist makes it much easier to use the camera&rsquo;s powerful zoom lens. When you press and hold the Zoom Framing Assist function button, the camera will automatically zoom out to include a wider angle of view, enabling you to more easily locate your moving subject on the LCD screen or through the electronic viewfinder. Released the button once you found the subject and you are ready to capture the perfect close-up moment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(7, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot SX50', 'gambar/powershot-sx50hs-b1.png', 1, 4750000, '<h2 class=\"red\">The Power to set your sights further</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">The PowerShot SX50 HS is equipped with an extremely powerful 50x (24 - 1200mm) optical zoom giving you true shooting versatility. The Intelligent Stabilizer feature ensures crisp, brilliant images at any zoom length. The camera\'s slim, compact body is proportioned in perfect relation to the giant zoom, while rounded corners with angled grips are a natural fit for the palm of your hand. An enhanced Zoom Framing Assist Seek and Lock buttons help you track and capture subjects for sharp super telephoto photography, and the new High Speed AF dramatically reduces lag time so you\'ll never miss a shot.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>12.1 megapixels CMOS sensor </span></li>\r\n<li><span>24 - 1200mm</span></li>\r\n<li><span>2.8\" Vari-angle LCD</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Zoom Framing Assist Seek and Lock</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">At maximum telephoto, it can be challenging to track a moving subject hence Zoom Framing Assist feature makes it much easier to use the camera\'s powerful zoom lens. When you press and hold the Zoom Framing Assist Seek button, the camera will automatically zoom out to include a wider angle of view, enabling you to more easily locate your moving subject. Once you find it, release the Seek button to return to its original zoom position. You may depress the Zoom Framing Assist Lock button to keep the subject in focus for that perfect close-up capture.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Intelligent IS (Image Stabilizer)</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The camera automatically selects the optimum IS for all situations allowing users to capture crystal-clear, picture-perfect moments whether if they are capturing photographs or video. <br /> <br /> The Intelligent IS eliminates shake by analyzing the motion of both the camera and subject, and identifies the shot type such as panning, macro or telephoto shot.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>High-speed AF</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The PowerShot SX50 HS is equipped with Canon\'s latest advancements in Autofocus (AF) technology. Canon\'s newly developed AF achieves a significant increase in speed, for a shooting experience that\'s spontaneous and natural. The remarkably responsive High Speed AF lets you capture up to 13 fps at full resolution with reduced lag time.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
(8, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot S110', 'gambar/powershot-s110-b9.png', 1, 3700000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">The Power to turn night into light</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">The PowerShot S110 is a compact, sophisticated digital camera incorporating the most advanced Canon technologies enabling advanced users and photo-enthusiasts with the power to create stunning images that stand out from the crowd. The trademark fast f/2.0 lens helps tackle difficult lighting and capture breathtaking portraits with beautiful, shallow depth-of-field. As automatic or manual as you need it to be, the PowerShot S110 is a serious photographic tool impressing even demanding pros. The PowerShot S110 is now available in white, black and silver.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>12.1 megapixels CMOS sensor </span></li>\r\n<li><span>F2.0</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Wi-Fi</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>WIFI</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The built-in WiFi wireless technology makes captured images and HD videos available easily for effortless sharing to friends and family. With the Canon CameraWindow app, the PowerShot S110 is able to directly connect to iOS and Android devices so captured images can be shared virtually anywhere. Whether sending them directly into these devices and / or upload onto Facebook, Twitter, YouTube and email. Users can also make use of the GPS functions to add GPS data onto the PowerShot S110\'s images and do wireless printing with any compatible printers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Control Ring</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The unique Control Ring feature allows instant, convenient adjustments of the Focus, Exposure, ISO, Step Zoom, or White Balance.. Located at the base of the lens barrel, the ring is more intuitive than other types of controls for many experienced photographers. The functions that can be assigned to the control ring vary with shooting mode, and you can set your preferences using the dedicated ring function selector button.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Large 3\" capacitive touchscreen LCD</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Using the same capacitive technology as today\'s popular mobile devices, this new screen is touch-sensitive and delivers intuitive touch panel operation. Two finger touch gestures (multi-touch) can be used for zooming into images and quick control settings can be accessed. The additional benefit of Touch AF makes it fast and easy to focus on any subject, by simply touching it on the screen.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(9, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot G15', 'gambar/powershot-g15-b1.png', 1, 4650000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">The Power to capture life</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">With the fastest* AF in Canon\'s history, the PowerShot G15 will inspire advanced amateurs who have embraced the G-Series to explore new realms of photographic expression, and give pros an excellent camera that complements their creative demands. <br /><br /><em>* For Canon compact digital cameras. As of Aug 20, 2012. A Canon survey</em>\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>12.1 megapixels CMOS sensor </span></li>\r\n<li><span>28 - 140mm</span></li>\r\n<li><span>F1.8 - 2.8</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>5x Wide-Angle Optical Zoom and 10x ZoomPlus</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">With a bright and fast f/1.8 lens, a 5x wide optical zoom (28 - 140mm) and a 10x Zoomplus built with the knowledge acquired over decades of Canon leadership in optical technology innovation, photographers can capture a wealth of subtle detail, even indoors and in dark scenes, and easily covers a full range of shooting situations.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>High-speed burst continuous shooting</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Utilizing the increased processing speed and power of the new Canon DIGIC 5 Imaging Processor, High-Speed Burst HQ makes it possible to capture fast action stills at full resolution during continuous shooting. The results are exceptionally high-quality images recorded in rapid sequence. In this mode, the PowerShot G15 can capture a maximum of 10fps in a single burst.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Compatibility with Canon Speedlite Flashes</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The PowerShot G15 gives you access to exciting EOS accessories including the Macro Light Adapter MLA-DC1, Macro Ring Light MR-14EX, and all of the Canon Speedlite flashes, long revered by professional photographers. The high output of Speedlite flashes brings out the depth and texture of your images in full, natural beauty.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(10, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot G1X', 'gambar/powershot-g15-b1.png', 0, 5750000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">The G Perfection is no coincidence</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Photographic excellence has arrived with the PowerShot G1 X, the most premium Canon compact camera that boasts of the largest sensor at 1.5&rdquo;.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>4x optical zoom</span></li>\r\n<li><span>14.3 megapixels high-sensitivity 1.5&rdquo; CMOS sensor</span></li>\r\n<li><span>14-bit RAW &amp; ISO 12800</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>1.5\" high-sensitivity CMOS sensor</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The large Canon\'s original 1.5\" CMOS sensor\'s rapid image capturing capability allows fast continuous shooting and autofocus even on moving subjects, making continuous high-speed shooting (4.5fps) at the full 14.3 megapixels possible.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Intelligent IS (Image Stabilizer)</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The camera automatically selects the optimum IS for all situations allowing users to capture crystal-clear, picture-perfect moments whether if they are capturing photographs or video.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">The Intelligent IS eliminates shake by analyzing the motion of both the camera and subject, and identifies the shot type such as panning, macro or telephoto shot.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>The professional touch</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Raise your craft to a higher level with the PowerShot G1 X which is highly compatible with a host of EOS accessories intended for all EOS series DSLR cameras.</p>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Optical underwater casing WP-DC44 is available.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(11, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'PowerShot D20', 'gambar/powershotd20-b7.png', 0, 3500000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span class=\"bold_text\"><strong> <span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\">Overview </span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 8pt; font-family: Verdana;\"><strong> <span class=\"bold_text\">Let the Adventure Begin.</span></strong><br /> Outdoorsy, adventurous types need to look no further for a camera that can handle it all. The PowerShot D20 digital camera is waterproof to 33 feet, temperature-resistant from 14Â&lsaquo;F to 104Â&lsaquo;F, shockproof up to 5.0 feet, and equipped with a GPS tracker. Slim and sturdy with a highly visible color layout, its buttons are operable even with gloved hands. Spectacular image quality is ensured with the 12.1 Megapixel High-Sensitivity CMOS sensor and DIGIC 4 Image Processor for excellent low-light performance, and a 5x Optical Zoom with 28mm Wide-Angle Lens that brings excitement to your imaging. A single touch and you\'ll be shooting incredibly vivid 1080p Full HD Video with full zooming capability. Lots of optional accessories take you deeper underwater and more.</span></p>'),
(12, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'IXUS140 HS', 'gambar/digital-ixus140-b9.png', 2, 1900000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">World&rsquo;s slimmest* 8x long zoom IXUS</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Widen your photographic range with the IXUS 140&rsquo;s 8x optical zoom lens. Matched by the convenience of a slim and compact design, the IXUS 140 is extremely easy to carry around as it will easily fit into pockets and purses, which makes it a suitable companion for holidays and parties. <br /> <br /><em>* as of 30 November 2012 in a Canon survey among digital compact cameras with a 8x zoom lens</em>\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>Wi-Fi</span></li>\r\n<li><span>28 - 224mm</span></li>\r\n<li><span>16x ZoomPlus</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Wi-Fi</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Instant transfer and sharing of your photographs and videos with your friends on smart devices and popular social network sites.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Eco Mode</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">By reducing the LCD screen brightness gradually until it switches off when the camera is not in use, the ECO mode saves battery consumption and allows you maximized photo opportunity - up to 30% more photos!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Spectacular Creative Filters</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Create upscale photographic effects with no special lenses required but in just one easy step through the creative filters options which include Fisheye Effect for the classic convex distortion; Toy Camera Effect that recreates the toy or pinhole camera look; and Monochrome that adds a distinct single-tone effect to your photos .</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
(13, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'IXUS 132', 'gambar/ixus132-b9.png', 3, 1350000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">Your Everyday Accessory</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Easy operability and reliable high-quality Canon performance are reasons enough to carry the IXUS 132 everywhere. You will fall in love with the attention-getting quality of the camera\'s distinctly sophisticated modern design. Choose from Silver, blue and pink.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>16 megapixels</span></li>\r\n<li><span>28 - 224mm</span></li>\r\n<li><span>2.7\" LCD screen</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Eco Mode</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">By reducing the LCD screen brightness gradually until it switches off when the camera is not in use, the ECO mode saves battery consumption and allows you maximized photo opportunity - up to 30% more photos!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>See further with 16x ZoomPlus</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Zoom in on the details of those dynamic architectural and scenic landscapes with the 16x ZoomPlus.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Spectacular Creative Filters</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Create upscale photographic effects with no special lenses required but in just one easy step through the creative filters options which include Fisheye Effect for the classic convex distortion; Toy Camera Effect that recreates the toy or pinhole camera look; and Monochrome that adds a distinct single-tone effect to your photos.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(14, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'IXUS 135', 'gambar/ixus135-b1.png', 1, 1650000, '<p>Garansi : datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">Stylishly Affordable</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Tell your story with style and share it with the world with the beautiful and connected IXUS 135. The new ECO Mode, conserve energy allowing more captured shots per charge and ensuring that you stay connected all the time even if the party lasts all night.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>16 megapixels</span></li>\r\n<li><span>16x ZoomPlus</span></li>\r\n<li><span>HD movie recording</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Capture HD Movie with dedicated Movie Button</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Switch to movie recording seamlessly with the dedicated movie button. There is literally no need to plan ahead, or search through menus on the LCD screen; simply press the button and recording begins when you feel the moment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Wifi</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Connect to a smart device or any compatible wireless devices for wireless transfer of images to social networking sites; to a PC or any compatible iOS&reg; or Android&trade; devices with the with the free download of the Canon CameraWindow app.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>See further with 16x ZoomPlus</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Zoom in on the details of those dynamic architectural and scenic landscapes with the 16x ZoomPlus.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(15, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'IXUS 255 HS', 'gambar/ixus255hs-b9.png', 2, 2300000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">Elegantly Smart</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Brimming with a full range of advanced Canon technologies, that automatically optimize the image quality of every shot, the IXUS 255 HS makes creating breathtakingly beautiful images effortlessly simple. The IXUS 255 HS comes in elegant black, silver and pink.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>12.1 megapixels high sensitivity CMOS sensor</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Wifi</span></li>\r\n<li><span>24 - 240mm</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Full HD Movie with dedicated Movie Button</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Switch to movie recording seamlessly with the dedicated movie button. There is literally no need to plan ahead, or search through menus on the LCD screen; simply press the button and recording begins when you feel the moment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Wifi</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Connect to a smart device or any compatible wireless devices for wireless transfer of images to social networking sites; to a PC or any compatible iOS&reg; or Android&trade; devices with the with the free download of the Canon CameraWindow app</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>See further with 20x ZoomPlus</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Zoom in on the details of those dynamic architectural and scenic landscapes with the 20x ZoomPlus.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br class=\"red\" />\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(16, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS M (18-55)', 'gambar/eos-m_b1.png', 2, 6500000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">Canon puts the quality of the EOS System in your pocket with the brand new EOS M. <br />(Available in black or red colours)</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Canon&rsquo;s first Digital Single Lens non-reflex camera, EOS M. The all new EOS M cumulate the fruits of Canon&rsquo;s EOS technology to create a revolutionary interchangeable lens camera in a compact form factor.<br /><br />Coupled with a multi touch-screen interface, EOS M is the most accessible EOS camera equipped with powerful imaging technologies like an 18 megapixel APS-C CMOS sensor and the DIGIC 5 imaging engine, providing the same level of photographic brilliance of a DSLR.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>Compact size and lightweight design</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Available with 2 newly developed EF-M lenses and compatible with all EF and EF-S lenses via an adapter</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Movie Servo AF enabled</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Compact, lightweight and mobile EOS</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Size and weight are dramatically reduced by replacing D-SLR camera&rsquo;s viewfinder / AF / AE / light-control functions with digital functions based on imaging elements.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Compatible with EOS lenses and accessories</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Existing EF &amp; EF-S lenses (via Mount Adapter EF-EOS M) and EOS accessories can be used. Existing Speedlites, GPS receiver GP-E2 and Remote controller RC-6 can be used.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Movie Servo AF</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Continuous auto-focus during movie recording is possible with all lenses (via Mount adapter EF-EOS M for EF / EF-S lenses). With STM lenses that are geared for movie shooting, users enjoy smooth, speedy quiet Servo AF on EOS M during movie shooting.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(17, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS M (22 + Adapter)', 'gambar/eos-m_b2.png', 3, 6950000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">Canon puts the quality of the EOS System in your pocket with the brand new EOS M. <br />(Available in black or red colours)</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Canon&rsquo;s first Digital Single Lens non-reflex camera, EOS M. The all new EOS M cumulate the fruits of Canon&rsquo;s EOS technology to create a revolutionary interchangeable lens camera in a compact form factor.<br /><br />Coupled with a multi touch-screen interface, EOS M is the most accessible EOS camera equipped with powerful imaging technologies like an 18 megapixel APS-C CMOS sensor and the DIGIC 5 imaging engine, providing the same level of photographic brilliance of a DSLR.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>Compact size and lightweight design</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Available with 2 newly developed EF-M lenses and compatible with all EF and EF-S lenses via an adapter</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Movie Servo AF enabled</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Compact, lightweight and mobile EOS</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Size and weight are dramatically reduced by replacing D-SLR camera&rsquo;s viewfinder / AF / AE / light-control functions with digital functions based on imaging elements.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Compatible with EOS lenses and accessories</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Existing EF &amp; EF-S lenses (via Mount Adapter EF-EOS M) and EOS accessories can be used. Existing Speedlites, GPS receiver GP-E2 and Remote controller RC-6 can be used.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Movie Servo AF</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Continuous auto-focus during movie recording is possible with all lenses (via Mount adapter EF-EOS M for EF / EF-S lenses). With STM lenses that are geared for movie shooting, users enjoy smooth, speedy quiet Servo AF on EOS M during movie shooting.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>'),
(18, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS M (18-55 + 22 + S90)', 'gambar/eos-m_b2-2.png', 2, 8000000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">Canon puts the quality of the EOS System in your pocket with the brand new EOS M. <br />(Available in black or red colours)</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Canon&rsquo;s first Digital Single Lens non-reflex camera, EOS M. The all new EOS M cumulate the fruits of Canon&rsquo;s EOS technology to create a revolutionary interchangeable lens camera in a compact form factor.<br /><br />Coupled with a multi touch-screen interface, EOS M is the most accessible EOS camera equipped with powerful imaging technologies like an 18 megapixel APS-C CMOS sensor and the DIGIC 5 imaging engine, providing the same level of photographic brilliance of a DSLR.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>Compact size and lightweight design</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Available with 2 newly developed EF-M lenses and compatible with all EF and EF-S lenses via an adapter</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Movie Servo AF enabled</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Compact, lightweight and mobile EOS</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Size and weight are dramatically reduced by replacing D-SLR camera&rsquo;s viewfinder / AF / AE / light-control functions with digital functions based on imaging elements.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Compatible with EOS lenses and accessories</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Existing EF &amp; EF-S lenses (via Mount Adapter EF-EOS M) and EOS accessories can be used. Existing Speedlites, GPS receiver GP-E2 and Remote controller RC-6 can be used.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Movie Servo AF</h2>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Continuous auto-focus during movie recording is possible with all lenses (via Mount adapter EF-EOS M for EF / EF-S lenses). With STM lenses that are geared for movie shooting, users enjoy smooth, speedy quiet Servo AF on EOS M during movie shooting.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>'),
(19, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS 1100D (18-55)', 'gambar/eos1100dkit-b9.png', 3, 4400000, '<p>Garansi: Datascrip<br /><br /><br /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Advanced, compact and affordable: your first steps into the world of DSLR photography, made simple with Canon EOS 1100D. </strong></span><br /><br /> Benefits<br /> Superior 12-megapixel image quality <br />On-screen Feature Guide <br />Creative Auto and Basic+ <br />HD video capture <br />ISO 100-6400 sensitivity <br />Wide-area 9-point AF system <br />63-zone iFCL exposure metering <br />6.8cm (2.7&rdquo;), 230,000-dot screen <br />Use with all EF and EF-S lenses <br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">12-megapixel resolution</span> </strong><br /><br /> Step up to DSLR image quality with a 12-megapixel APS-C-sized sensor. A 14-bit DIGIC 4 image processor provides up to 3.2fps continuous shooting and images that are packed with detail and tonal range. <br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Intuitive, on-screen feature guide </span></strong><br /><br /> The EOS 1100D&rsquo;s Feature Guide provides descriptions of many of the camera&rsquo;s functions, as well as advice on how to use them in your own photography. <br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Easy to use Scene modes and Basic+</span> </strong><br /><br /> Theme-based Scene modes automatically pick the most suitable exposure, focus and drive-mode settings for the subject being photographed, while Creative Auto mode portrays adjustable functions in an easy to understand way. With Canon&rsquo;s Basic + technology, the look and feel of these basic auto modes can be fine-tuned according to ambience and lighting type. <br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">HD EOS Movie mode</span> </strong><br /><br /> Shoot stunning HD video at 25 or 30fps, with automatic exposure control leaving you free to concentrate on the action. Footage can be edited on your PC or Mac, or played directly on an HD TV via the camera&rsquo;s HDMI connection. <br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">ISO 100-6400 sensitivity</span> </strong><br /><br /> Low-light shooting without flash is possible thanks to the EOS 1100D&rsquo;s ISO 100-6400 sensitivity range. The camera&rsquo;s 14-bit DIGIC 4 processor helps to control noise and maintain image quality. <br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Wide-area 9-point AF system</span> </strong><br /><br /> The EOS 1100D focuses quickly and accurately on static and moving subjects, thanks to nine AF points, spread out across the frame. A central cross-type AF point is sensitive to both horizontal and vertical lines <br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">63-zone iFCL exposure metering</span> </strong><br /><br /> Advanced iFCL exposure metering dissects a scene into 63-zones before analyzing it to find the perfect combination of shutter speed, aperture and ISO <br /><br /> <br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Use with all EF and EF-S lenses</span> </strong><br /><br /> The EOS 1100D is supported by the complete range of EOS lenses and accessories: flashguns, remote releases and a system of more than 60 lenses trusted by professional photographers the world over.</p>'),
(20, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS 600D ', 'gambar/eos600d-body-b1.png', 1, 4800000, '<p>Garansi: Datascrip<br /><br /><br />The EOS 600D is powered by an 18-megapixel high image quality CMOS sensor and the powerful DIGIC 4 image processor. Features like Scene Intelligent Auto, Basic+ and Feature Guide make it simple to achieve full control over creative functions. The advanced Creative are integrated into the EOS 600D, as well as Full HD video recording and Video Snapshot. <br /><br /> 18.0 megapixel APS-C size CMOS sensor<br /> ISO 100-6400, expandable to 12800<br /> Full HD recording in 24, 25 and 30fps<br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> Class-leading 18.0-megapixel CMOS sensor</span></strong><br /><br /> In the spirit of Canon\'s imaging supremacy, the EOS 600D adopts a generous 18-megapixel CMOS (APS-C-sized) sensor that empowers you to take all manner of scenes from vast, breathtaking landscapes to close-up wildlife shots in explicit detail. Having a massive 18-megapixel resolution also means that you can still turn your photos into gallery exhibits even after cropping them.<br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 3-inch wide Vari-Angle clear view LCD monitor</span></strong><br /><br /> For exceptional recording and playback of images, the EOS 600D employs a crisp 3-inch wide Vari-Angle Clear View LCD monitor that contains over a million dots. The nifty Vari-Angle screen is also a welcome addition for curious shutterbugs looking to discover fresh framing perspectives, as the specially designed hinge allows it to be swivelled in almost any angle.<br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Scene Intelligent Auto</span></strong><br /><br /> Fresh out of Canon\'s factory of innovation is the Scene Intelligent Auto mode, a fully automatic shooting mode that takes total advantage of the EOS Scene Detection System, an integrated system that analyzes every element of a scene including a person\'s face, and/or the image\'s brightness, movement, contrast, colour, distance and more. This information is then expertly evaluated by Scene Intelligent Auto to produce beautiful exposures that truly capture the essence of their surroundings.</p>'),
(21, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS 650D', 'gambar/eos650d-b6.png', 1, 5800000, '<p>Garansi: Datascrip<br /><br /><br />The EOS 650D promises unparalleled performance with the world\'s* first intuitive touch screen (vari-angle) interface for set-shoot-view convenience. Its Auto-focus (AF) System is precise with a new 9-point all cross-type AF backed by a new Hybrid CMOS AF System. AF speeds are dramatically increased while focusing on live view and movie shooting modes.<br /><br /> ISO 100-12800, expandable to 25600<br /> Handheld Night Scene<br /> Continuous AF in Movie Mode<br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> World\'s first Vari-Angle Clear View LCD II Touch Monitor</span></strong><br /><br /> With the intuitive set-shoot-view vari-angle LCD touch screen monitor, it\'s easy to adjust exposure and shutter speeds quickly. Auto-focusing in live view mode is activated by tapping the subject on the LCD. A Touch Shutter option activates the shutter on tapping on the area to be focused. Perform familiar multi-touch gestures to zoom in and out of shots, view images and flip pages.<br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hybrid CMOS AF System</span></strong><br /> <br /> During live view and movie shooting, EOS 650D uses both conventional Contrast AF and new Phase Difference AF in conjunction with continuous AF to quickly focus on a subject even before the shutter is pressed. <br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Choose from 4 different AF methods:</span></strong><br /><br /> &middot; Face + tracking<br /> &middot; rack a face, even in side profile with the EOS 650D. AF points can also be switched simply by touching the subject on the LCD monitor<br /><br /> &middot; FlexiZone &ndash; Multi<br /> &middot; The EOS 650D intuitively selects the appropriate focus from 31 AF points. Touch the LCD monitor on any of the 9 AF zones to fine-tune auto focus.<br /> <br /> &middot; FlexiZone &ndash; Single<br /> &middot; Touch anywhere on the LCD monitor to move the AF point<br /> <br /> &middot; Quick mode<br /> &middot; Select any of the 9 AF point unlike conventional focus mechanisms by selecting the area on the LCD panel <br /><br /> Enhanced Movie shooting with Movie Servo AF Movie servo is possible with all lenses. But the new EF-S18-135mm f/3.5-5.6 IS STM lens is geared for movie shooting; users enjoy smooth, speedy and quiet Servo AF on EOS 650D during movie shooting.</p>'),
(22, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS 600D (18-135)', 'gambar/eos600d-kit2-b4.png', 1, 7650000, '<p>Garansi: Datascrip<br /><br /><br />The EOS 600D is powered by an 18-megapixel high image quality CMOS sensor and the powerful DIGIC 4 image processor. Features like Scene Intelligent Auto, Basic+ and Feature Guide make it simple to achieve full control over creative functions. The advanced Creative are integrated into the EOS 600D, as well as Full HD video recording and Video Snapshot. <br /><br /> 18.0 megapixel APS-C size CMOS sensor<br /> ISO 100-6400, expandable to 12800<br /> Full HD recording in 24, 25 and 30fps<br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> Class-leading 18.0-megapixel CMOS sensor</span></strong><br /><br /> In the spirit of Canon\'s imaging supremacy, the EOS 600D adopts a generous 18-megapixel CMOS (APS-C-sized) sensor that empowers you to take all manner of scenes from vast, breathtaking landscapes to close-up wildlife shots in explicit detail. Having a massive 18-megapixel resolution also means that you can still turn your photos into gallery exhibits even after cropping them.<br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3-inch wide Vari-Angle clear view LCD monitor</span></strong><br /><br /> For exceptional recording and playback of images, the EOS 600D employs a crisp 3-inch wide Vari-Angle Clear View LCD monitor that contains over a million dots. The nifty Vari-Angle screen is also a welcome addition for curious shutterbugs looking to discover fresh framing perspectives, as the specially designed hinge allows it to be swivelled in almost any angle.<br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Scene Intelligent Auto</span></strong><br /><br /> Fresh out of Canon\'s factory of innovation is the Scene Intelligent Auto mode, a fully automatic shooting mode that takes total advantage of the EOS Scene Detection System, an integrated system that analyzes every element of a scene including a person\'s face, and/or the image\'s brightness, movement, contrast, colour, distance and more. This information is then expertly evaluated by Scene Intelligent Auto to produce beautiful exposures that truly capture the essence of their surroundings.</p>'),
(23, 'Handycam', 'Sony', 'DCR PJ6', 'gambar/pj6.jpg', 1, 3500000, '<p>Garansi : Sony Indonesia</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 class=\"HeaderText\">HandyCam&reg; Camcorder-Flash/Memory Stick</h1>\r\n<div class=\"ProductAvailibility\"><span>Model:</span>\r\n<h2 class=\"HeaderText\">DCR-PJ6E</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"BodyText\">Share your memories virtually anywhere using the SD Handycam&reg; Camcorder\'s built-in, high-contrast projector. This mobile theatre can project up to a 60\" (diag.) image on any flat surface, and with powerful stereo speakers, you\'ll hear all the action.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"featuresList BodyText\">\r\n<li>1/8&rdquo; 800K <span class=\"GlossaryLink\">pixel</span> <span class=\"GlossaryLink\">CCD</span></li>\r\n<li>Sony Lens 60x <span class=\"GlossaryLink\">optical zoom</span></li>\r\n<li>70x Extended Zoom</li>\r\n<li>SteadyShot</li>\r\n<li>2.7&rdquo; Wide <span class=\"GlossaryLink\">Clear Photo LCD</span></li>\r\n<li>Built-in Projector</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Picture Motion Browser (PMB)</span> <br /> The bundled PMB software offers useful post-shooting solutions such as importing videos and images from the Handycam&reg; camcorder, managing and viewing imported contents, all in an intuitive user interface.</td>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Compact And Light Body</span> <br /> With built-in projector incorporated within an incredibly slim and compact body, shooting and sharing your cherished memories is made possible, anytime, anywhere.</td>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Embedded PMB Portable</span> <br /> Without having to manually install any additional software, the embedded PMB portable software in the DCR-PJ6E allows you to quickly and easily upload your creations to websites such as Facebook and YouTube virtually from any PC, or even a Mac.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Memory Card Slot Compatibility (MS/SD)</span> <br /> DCR-PJ6E is compatible with two memory cards, allowing you to fully enjoy your shooting experience with Handycam.</td>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Face-Detection Technology</span> <br /> Face Detection technology automatically detects faces, optimises focus exposure and colour for the best result.</td>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Built-in LED Video Light</span> <br /> With the built-in LED video light. DCR-PJ6E allows you to capture brillient quality videos and photos even in a dark environment.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>');
