(24, 'Handycam', 'Sony', 'DCR SX22', 'gambar/sx22.jpg', 1, 1900000, '<p>Garansi : Sony Indonesia</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1 class=\"HeaderText\">HandyCam&reg; Camcorder-Flash/Memory Stick</h1>\r\n<div class=\"ProductAvailibility\"><span>Model:</span>\r\n<h2 class=\"HeaderText\">DCR-SX22E/S</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"BodyText\">Enjoy easy shooting with the light and compact Standard Definition Memory Stick Camcorder. It features an improved 60x Optical Zoom (70x Extended Zoom), SteadyShot for steadier shoots and intelligent AUTO makes capturing a great shoot easy in any conditions.</p>\r\n<ul class=\"featuresList BodyText\">\r\n<li>1/8&rdquo; 800K <span class=\"GlossaryLink\">pixel</span> <span class=\"GlossaryLink\">CCD</span></li>\r\n<li>Sony Lens 60x <span class=\"GlossaryLink\">optical zoom</span></li>\r\n<li>70x Extended Zoom</li>\r\n<li>SteadyShot</li>\r\n<li>2.7&rdquo; Wide <span class=\"GlossaryLink\">Clear Photo LCD</span></li>\r\n<li>PMB portable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Picture Motion<br />Browser (PMB)</span> <br /> Share your videos easily with PMB Portable, already embedded in your Handycam&reg;. PMB Portable lets you upload videos to Facebook and YouTube easily when you connect your Handycam&reg; to a computer via a USB cable &ndash; no installation required.\r\n<p>For advanced importing options, check out the full version of PMB in the CD-ROM provided with every Handycam&reg;.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Direct Copy</span> <br /> With Direct Copy, you can also back up videos directly onto your external hard drive, via a USB adapter.</td>\r\n<td class=\"FeatureList\"><span class=\"FeatureListHeader\">Dual-Compatibility Memory Card Slot</span> <br /> Shoot and store more on your Handycam&reg; with a memory card slot that\'s compatible with both MS and SD cards.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>'),
(25, 'Handycam', 'Canon', 'Legria HF R36', 'gambar/legriafs36-b1.png', 1, 4800000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">The LEGRIA HF R36 lets you record professional videos with ease. Working silently and steadily, it captures brilliant high-definition movies and lets you share them easily, no matter where you are.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>Cinema Style</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Built-in Wi-Fi &amp; MP4 recording</span></li>\r\n<li><span>Intelligent IS</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>Cinema Style</h2>\r\n<div class=\"hr\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Create dramatic movies like never before with revolutionary Cinema Style comprising of Story Creator, Cinema-look filters and Touch Decoration.<br /> <br /> Story Creator helps users to create \"video stories\" with a sense of narrative and pacing. Choose from five preset themes and recommended story scenes on the camcorder.<br /> <br /> Cinema-look filters compensate colour, gamma and other aspects of the image quality. Create professional looking video easily with 9 different \"looks\" (Standard / Vivid / Dream / Cool / Nostalgic / Sepia / Old Movies / Memory / Dramatic B &amp; W).<br /> <br /> Touch Decoration superimposes decorations added by users through the touch panel onto the images and then records the resulting images. Users can select decoration settings using pen &amp; stamp, animation, date / time &amp; title or image mix (mixed image selection).</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>Built-in Wi-Fi &amp; MP4 recording</h2>\r\n<div class=\"hr\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Built-in Wi-Fi conforms to 802.11 b/g/n wireless specifications. Recorded videos can be transferred to Windows PC running bundled Network Utility software or to a FTP server. Movies can also be recorded in MP4 format or converted from existing footage and be uploaded to social networking sites natively, via built-in Wi-Fi, through a dedicated iPhone app.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>Intelligent IS</h2>\r\n<div class=\"hr\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Intelligent IS automatically selects and switches among 4 types of IS (Dynamic IS, Macro IS, Powered IS, Tripod) depending on shooting conditions. Users are now free to concentrate on shooting a scene and let the camcorder decide automatically on the best IS mode for the scene.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n</div>'),
(26, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS 650D (18-135)', 'gambar/eos650d-b10.png', 0, 8750000, '<p>Garansi: Datascrip<br /><br /><br />The EOS 650D promises unparalleled performance with the world\'s* first intuitive touch screen (vari-angle) interface for set-shoot-view convenience. Its Auto-focus (AF) System is precise with a new 9-point all cross-type AF backed by a new Hybrid CMOS AF System. AF speeds are dramatically increased while focusing on live view and movie shooting modes.<br /><br /> ISO 100-12800, expandable to 25600<br /> Handheld Night Scene<br /> Continuous AF in Movie Mode<br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">World\'s first Vari-Angle Clear View LCD II Touch Monitor</span></strong><br /><br /> With the intuitive set-shoot-view vari-angle LCD touch screen monitor, it\'s easy to adjust exposure and shutter speeds quickly. Auto-focusing in live view mode is activated by tapping the subject on the LCD. A Touch Shutter option activates the shutter on tapping on the area to be focused. Perform familiar multi-touch gestures to zoom in and out of shots, view images and flip pages.<br /><br /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hybrid CMOS AF System</span></strong><br /> <br /> During live view and movie shooting, EOS 650D uses both conventional Contrast AF and new Phase Difference AF in conjunction with continuous AF to quickly focus on a subject even before the shutter is pressed. <br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> Choose from 4 different AF methods:</span></strong><br /><br /> &middot; Face + tracking<br /> &middot; rack a face, even in side profile with the EOS 650D. AF points can also be switched simply by touching the subject on the LCD monitor<br /><br /> &middot; FlexiZone &ndash; Multi<br /> &middot; The EOS 650D intuitively selects the appropriate focus from 31 AF points. Touch the LCD monitor on any of the 9 AF zones to fine-tune auto focus.<br /> <br /> &middot; FlexiZone &ndash; Single<br /> &middot; Touch anywhere on the LCD monitor to move the AF point<br /> <br /> &middot; Quick mode<br /> &middot; Select any of the 9 AF point unlike conventional focus mechanisms by selecting the area on the LCD panel <br /><br /> Enhanced Movie shooting with Movie Servo AF Movie servo is possible with all lenses. But the new EF-S18-135mm f/3.5-5.6 IS STM lens is geared for movie shooting; users enjoy smooth, speedy and quiet Servo AF on EOS 650D during movie shooting.</p>'),
(27, 'Kamera', 'Canon', 'EOS 60D', 'gambar/eos60d-body-b1.png', 1, 7200000, '<p>Garansi : Datascrip</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"red\">A New Perspective</h2>\r\n<hr class=\"white\" />\r\n<div class=\"left onecolumn\">Designed to realize your perfect shot, the 60D&rsquo;s pairing of two state-of-the-art sensor and image processor allows it to capture action at a slick 5.3fps while the shutter speed range of 1/8000 sec ensures that nothing escapes your vision.\r\n<ul class=\"product_listing\">\r\n<li><span>18.0 megapixel APS-C size CMOS sensor</span></li>\r\n<li><span>In-camera post processing</span></li>\r\n<li><span>3-inch wide Vari-Angle LCD</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn\">\r\n<h2>18-megapixel sensor</h2>\r\n<img src=\"http://media.canon-asia.com/v3.5media/products/digital_cameras/eos60dkit-efs18-55/eos-60d18megapixel.jpg\" alt=\"EOS 60D Kit (EF S18-55)\" width=\"209\" height=\"100\" />\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Powered by a cutting-edge 18-megapixel APS-C sized CMOS sensor and dynamic DIGIC 4 processor, the EOS 60D leads the pack at rendering the finest colour gradations and the tiniest image details. The exceptional noise reduction feature lets you recreate your favourite scenes with greater finesse even in dimly-lit conditions.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn \">\r\n<h2>3-inch wide Vari-Angle LCD</h2>\r\n<img src=\"http://media.canon-asia.com/v3.5media/products/digital_cameras/eos60dkit-efs18-55/eos-60dvarianglelcd.jpg\" alt=\"EOS 60D Kit (EF S18-55)\" width=\"209\" height=\"100\" />\r\n<p class=\"justify\">Experience a whole new level of compositional freedom with the 3-inch wide Vari-Angle Clear View LCD. The multi-directional swivel of the screen (540&deg;), coupled with the high resolution of 1.04 million dots, empowers you to defy photographic conventions by snapping shots from previously challenging physical angles.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left inneronecolumn lastcolumn\">\r\n<h2>In-camera post processing</h2>\r\n<img src=\"http://media.canon-asia.com/v3.5media/products/digital_cameras/eos60dkit-efs18-55/eos-incamerapostprocessing.jpg\" alt=\"EOS 60D Kit (EF S18-55)\" width=\"209\" height=\"100\" />\r\n<p class=\"justify\">With a bevy of post-processing features to utilize including creative filters, white balance, picture style and brightness, the mood of your scene can be accentuated to fit your every visual whim. Enjoy the flexibility of sprucing up your exposures anytime, anywhere, without the hassle of external editing programs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>'),
